<s> This prevents us from implementing long term, cooperative transactions on top of the version control mechanism envisaged in WEB-DAV Response: The transaction protocol being worked in W3C and IETF will address this requirement Reposte: Duh! What we are asking for is different.  </s>
<s> Do we need to explain this or refer you folks to several papers that describe the concept of environments/contexts in cooperative transaction processing.  </s>
