<s> To consider adding such a requirement, you need to resolve several questions: What features do you want to support with this context information?  </s>
<s> Why do we need to have WebDAV clients and servers supporting this information?  </s>
<s> Why are cookies insufficient?  </s>
<s> Perhaps posting the papers references you mentioned would help me to better understand your position.  </s>
<s> Right now all I'm hearing is "we gotta have it" without (to my mind) really understanding either "it" or why it is so necessary.  </s>
<s> I have to concur that generalized transaction support should not be pursued by this working group.  </s>
